
Module Font::TFM:

	Read and work with TeX font metric information, stored in .tfm
	files.

Installation:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make install

Use:

	use Font::TFM;  
	my $cmr = new Font::TFM "cmr10";
	print $cmr->width("A"), ", ", $cmr->kern('Wo'), "\n";

